h3. Problem
REST call only shows one author in the page history JSON result when a version has multiple authors 

h3. Environment
Confluence server

h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Install Confluence 7.4.0 server
# Create two users (admin and test1)
# Log in Confluence as test1 then create a test page, publish the page
# Edit the same page as test1 and admin at the same time
#- You will see the following result in the page history (version 2 has two authors):
!page_history.png|width=500! 
# Send the REST call
{code:java}
GET http://localhost:6740/c740/rest/api/content/5439490/history HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Basic admin:admin
{code}
# There is only one author (admin) in the result
{code:java}
{
